{"title":"centos下修改用户密码","date":"2017-07-01T16:56:13.000Z","author":"许盛","excerpt":"<p>使用 <code>passwd</code> 命令可以用来修改用户密码。</p>","slug":"centos下修改用户密码","comments":true,"tags":["linux"],"categories":["linux"],"updated":"2018-08-23T09:23:13.686Z","content":"<p>使用 <code>passwd</code> 命令可以用来修改用户密码。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ passwd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>输入以上命令后回车，即可直接输入旧密码以及新密码，修改当前用户的密码</p>\n<hr>\n<p>对于<code>root</code>用户来说，可以直接修改其他用户的密码：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ passwd &lt;user_name&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>回车后直接输入新密码即可。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"centos 下查看本机公网IP","slug":"centos下查看本机公网IP"},"next":{"title":"2017半载小记","slug":"2017半载小记"},"link":"/post/centos下修改用户密码"}